    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997.2-generation Carrera S is a definitive example of mechanical precision, featuring the 3.8L Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) flat-six engine that delivers a linear power band and exceptional throttle response. The drivetrain is anchored by a seven-speed PDK dual-clutch transmission and a mechanical limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), the chassis remains perfectly composed under high lateral loads. This vehicle presents in showroom condition; the factory cosmoline is still visible on the undercarriage, and there is zero evidence of bore scoring or hydraulic weeping. A true turn-key enthusiast piece with rigorous service documentation and flawless compression across all cylinders.",
